<title>Subgoals for writing functions:</title>
    <p>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <p>Define and initialize global variables</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Write function header with function name and parameters (must include () even without
                    parameters)</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>Optional -- Set default values for parameters</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Write function body</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>Distinguish between global and local variables based on indentation</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Determine what to return, if anything, to call site</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Call function with appropriate arguments</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </p>